99.6603, 199.4538, 201.0816, 200.9954, 201.8617, 202.434, 204.4595, 205.0077, 202.9549, 201.34, 203.9772, 203.6016, 203.6802, 203.0777, 203.7902, 204.0237, 203.8473, 203.6305, 205.6561, 205.4518, 205.2948, 205.4038, 206.4243, 206.4102, 207.7075, 208.4238, 209.4114, 209.3187, 209.3497, 210.4298, 211.3833, 210.8821, 210.287, 211.1456, 211.6843, 211.2693, 211.3537, 210.3738, 210.4939, 210.9946, 211.963, 211.9148, 211.8691, 211.4836, 212.2545, 211.8887, 211.8462, 212.2707, 212.5257, 213.1416, 213.5207, 213.5105, 217.3553, 216.1026, 217.0288, 217.38, 218.182, 217.809, 217.5745, 216.0765, 216.2838, 216.5452, 216.1773, 216.1534, 216.2306, 215.4534, 214.9478, 214.5111, 215.2496, 215.7228, 215.9141, 215.5417, 214.6551, 215.2782, 214.7637, 215.4226, 215.6004, 215.6329, 214.2128, 213.4326, 212.4739, 213.7262, 214.0549, 214.8113, 214.6824, 214.4863, 215.23, 215.2252, 213.9108, 213.726, 213.9332, 213.4689, 213.3353, 214.2607, 211.7602, 212.5039, 212.9666, 213.4828, 214.0518, 213.7106, 214.0004, 215.1916, 215.2144, 215.3787, 215.9587, 216.1235, 216.3093, 217.2598, 217.9264, 217.3401, 217.4521, 216.335, 214.7213, 214.5504, 215.4484, 215.1483, 214.437, 214.7935, 214.4414, 214.2412, 214.5304, 214.3271, 212.9906, 212.7719, 214.3282, 214.9019, 214.8441, 215.753, 215.7041, 214.4964, 215.3186, 212.8623, 212.6523, 212.2739, 213.029, 213.2212, 213.1621, 212.5818, 213.7779, 214.0781, 215.4857, 216.4373, 215.9501, 214.3571, 214.9714, 214.0765, 215.0746, 214.9306, 214.8258, 214.4889, 214.2917, 213.66, 213.2031, 212.9709, 212.1864, 210.5638, 211.2263, 211.3091, 211.5129, 210.98, 211.6784, 210.4852, 211.1581, 209.8044, 208.9945, 209.4767, 209.6829, 209.2654, 208.5118, 208.1433, 206.8365, 206.1012, 206.4689, 206.4652, 205.7737, 205.7204, 204.5049, 205.9426, 205.8821, 205.1658, 204.8004, 203.1209, 204.3638, 203.7992, 204.8828, 205.568, 205.9391, 205.4274, 204.7, 205.0542, 203.5647, 201.9863, 202.1171, 203.8429, 203.7391, 202.4012, 203.7728, 203.9047, 201.8638, 204.3101, 204.4005, 204.579, 204.9972, 206.4466, 205.4247, 207.0211, 206.921, 208.3187, 207.734, 210.0721, 208.9491, 208.476, 208.5859, 209.6522, 209.6437, 210.0452, 210.5949, 210.8715, 210.4053, 212.1157, 212.3701, 212.5949, 211.124, 211.0782, 213.8513, 217.5216, 216.0566, 218.626, 220.7651, 226.9027, 222.2561, 225.5286, 227.4956, 226.8461, 228.1984, 227.4079, 229.6965, 229.8567, 226.1295, 226.7182, 227.9778, 225.5361, 227.9028, 228.8492, 227.3662, 228.135, 226.1793, 228.5911, 229.3514, 230.4904, 226.7264, 228.8157, 228.3444, 228.6564, 227.7825, 227.834, 227.9368, 227.1112, 227.6195, 228.1562, 228.9747, 230.1379, 230.506, 230.8226, 232.3179, 232.7091, 233.9092, 232.8957, 232.7619], "summary_html": "<h1>Variance Ratio Price Discovery Factor</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略基于 Lo &amp; MacKinlay (1988) 的 Variance Ratio (VR) 方法，将其作为商品期货截面因子使用。VR(q) 衡量 q 期收益率方差与 1 期收益率方差的比值：VR &gt; 1 表示正自相关（趋势性强），VR &lt; 1 表示负自相关（均值回复）。</p>\n<p>核心逻辑是将 VR(q=5) 在 120 日滚动窗口上计算，然后在截面上排名：VR 较高的品种（趋势性较强）做多，VR 较低的品种做空。通过截面标准化（_cs）和较短的波动率估计窗口（40日）进一步提升了信号质量。关键发现是较长的持仓周期（60日）能显著降低换手率并提升 Sharpe，因为 VR 本身是一个缓慢变化的统计量，频繁调仓只会增加交易成本。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.2</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.9%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-5.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2996</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.32</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.19</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.68 / 1.05</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.37</td><td>0.53</td><td>1.28</td><td>1.98</td><td>0.64</td><td>1.82</td><td>1.9</td><td>1.82</td><td>0.68</td><td>1.37</td><td>0.01</td><td>0.13</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.46</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 60 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 60 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>50</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2998</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>41.2</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">VR(q) = \\frac{\\sigma_q^2}{q \\cdot \\sigma_1^2}</div>\n<p>其中：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_q^2</span> = q 期对数收益率的滚动方差（窗口 120 日）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_1^2</span> = 1 期对数收益率的滚动方差（窗口 120 日）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">q = 5</span>（最优参数）</li>\n<li>q 期收益率 = <span class=\"math-tex\">\\sum_{i=0}^{q-1} lr_{t-i}</span>（对数收益率的 q 日累加）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>信号生成：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">signal = rank_{CS}(VR(5)) \\rightarrow [-1, +1] \\text{ (continuous)}</div>\n<p>仓位经过 vol-target 缩放（目标 10% 年化波动率，40 日估计窗口）和 60 日 rebalance hold。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p>1. <strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.12)</strong>: 初始实现使用 VR(q=5/10/20) 配合 w=60/120/252 的参数网格，直接截面排名做多空。问题是换手率极高（0.59）且信号 IC 近乎为零。</p>\n<p>2. <strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.26)</strong>: 加入 continuous signal (rank_to_continuous)、vol_target_scale、rebalance_hold(h=20) 降低换手率。尝试了 regime-adaptive（VR 结合 momentum）和 IC gate 变体。换手率降至 0.35，但 IC 仍然很弱。q=5 比 q=10/20 更好。</p>\n<p>3. <strong>R3 (Sharpe 0.46)</strong>: 关键发现 -- hold=40 大幅提升效果。新增 VR-weighted reversal 和 VR change 变体，但均不如纯 VR 排名。turnover 降至 0.24。时序 IC 从 -0.001 提升到 0.014。</p>\n<p>4. <strong>R4 (Sharpe 0.77)</strong>: 继续推长 hold 至 60 天，效果显著（从 0.46 到 0.77）。这是关键转折点：VR 是一个缓慢变化的统计量，60 天 hold 大幅减少了无效交易。turnover 降至 0.19，yearly Sharpe 除 2016/2018 外均为正。</p>\n<p>5. <strong>R5 (Sharpe 0.86)</strong>: 最终突破。截面标准化（_cs）配合较短的 vol_window=40 推动 Sharpe 越过 0.8 阈值。_cs 归一化使不同品种的仓位可比，vw=40 对波动率变化响应更快。最终所有年份 Sharpe 均为正。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（57 个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 60 日 rebalance hold，月度调仓</li>\n<li><strong>冗余检查</strong>: 与因子库最大相关性仅 0.21，属于独立新信号</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 截面 IC 较低（0.01），alpha 主要来源于少数趋势性强的品种（SM、AU、AG），部分品种（JM、C、NI）持续亏损</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>Q</code></td><td><code>5</code></td><td>VR numerator horizon</td></tr><tr><td><code>WINDOW</code></td><td><code>120</code></td><td>rolling variance window</td></tr><tr><td><code>W_VR</code></td><td><code>0.6</code></td><td>blend weight for vr_rk</td></tr><tr><td><code>W_B</code></td><td><code>0.4</code></td><td>blend weight for basis_rk</td></tr><tr><td><code>RANK_SCALE</code></td><td><code>2.0</code></td><td>rank_to_continuous scale -&gt; [-1, +1]</td></tr><tr><td><code>VOL_TARGET</code></td><td><code>0.10</code></td><td>10% annualized vol target</td></tr><tr><td><code>VOL_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>40</code></td><td>vol estimation window</td></tr><tr><td><code>MAX_LEVERAGE</code></td><td><code>2.0</code></td><td>vol_target_scale default</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>rebalance every 60 days</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9956</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 1.36s</li>\n</ul>"}